  "about_item": [
    "DESIGNED FOR STANDALONE USE OR YOUR 54-INCH CRATES – Precision-sized at 51\"×33\" to fit standard 37×54 wire crates and kennels wall-to-wall. Unlike universal beds that leave gaps or slide around, this bed locks in place with full coverage. Slides easily through the crate door. Works equally well as a stand-alone bed in the bedroom, living room, or anywhere your dog sleeps. Built for large dogs 90–150+ pounds who deserve real comfort in every space.",
    "PROFESSIONAL HIGH-DENSITY MEMORY FOAM THAT WON'T GO FLAT – Our orthopedic 45D foam is 60% denser than standard dog beds, maintaining its shape year after year while lower-density foam flattens. Engineered profile allows dogs to sit upright in crates (unlike 9\" beds that force hunching). Quality mattress technology means better support without excessive thickness. Perfect for Great Danes, Mastiffs, Saint Bernards, senior dogs, and breeds needing joint comfort.",
    "TRULY WASHABLE WITH REAL WATERPROOF PROTECTION – Removable plush cover machine washes weekly if needed. Our separate waterproof liner is a true barrier — not a spray coating that cracks and peels after a few washes. The liner continuously protects the memory foam core from accidents, drool, and moisture so the support layer stays clean and effective for years.",
    "BUILT FOR GIANT BREEDS BUT LOVED BY ALL SIZES – Supports extra large and giant breed dogs up to 150+ pounds without bottoming out. The generous 51\"×33\" size also works great for medium dogs who love to sprawl or multi-dog households. Anti-slip bottom keeps the bed secure whether inside a crate, kennel, or on hardwood, tile, or carpet.",
    "MIDWEST FAMILY-OWNED QUALITY – Premium polyester quilted fabric. Reinforced edges and heavy-duty zipper built for big dogs. Arrives vacuum-compressed (allow 24–48 hours to fully expand). Designed in the USA by Farmhouse Pet Supply.",
    "10-YEAR WARRANTY — CERTIFIED SAFE & BUILT TO LAST — Backed by a 10-year limited warranty on the foam core because we build it to last, not just to sell. CertiPUR-US and OEKO-TEX certified memory foam and fabric, free of harmful chemicals and off-gassing. Your dog deserves furniture you can trust."
  ],
