      {
        "position": 1,
        "title": "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ A purchase you can feel good about!",
        "text": "I wanted something that would help give more support for my dogs, and this bed does just that! I also loved the fact that I am buying this bed from a small business in the US. I would much rather put my money toward a company that genuinely cares about quality than buy a cheap bed that will not last. You can tell a lot more thought and care went into this bed. Honestly, it's so comfortable that even I like laying on it!For anyone on the fence, I would say this: if you want to give your dog the best comfort possible and a better chance at a high-quality life, this bed is a purchase you can feel good about. If your dog means the world to you like mine do, this bed is worth the investment. Our dogs give us so much love every day, and they deserve a place to rest that gives that love right back.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "April 14, 2026",
